title: Open Air Episode 5 A Week in Wyoming
description: It's back to business as usual for Cheryl Maas and her Open Air web series -- ripping pow lines in Jackson with Sarka Pancochova and legend Bryan Iguchi. More progressive backcountry riding from Cheryl in this episode, see her land a Cab double underflip!!! Check it out.
